                                 sum of the two previous numbers.</feedback>
        <feedback TYPE="Teacher">It looks like the student saw a difference pattern of 0, 1,1, 3,3, but
                                 it's Fibonacci.</feedback>
    </response>
    <response SCORE="0" EVIDENCEVAL="0">
        <observable ANY="true"/>
        <feedback TYPE="Student">Sorry, that was incorrect. This is a Fibonacci sequence.  Each new number is the
                                 sum of the two previous numbers.</feedback>
        <feedback TYPE="Teacher">The student got this item incorrect. Not sure what the problem is</feedback>
    </response>
</key>	
